high_descs: Go right and forward to the oven.
Take the pan from the left of the stove top.
Turn around, go forward, turn left after the dishwasher, go forward to the counter to the right of the dishwasher.
Put the pan on the counter.
Go left to the sink, face the sink.
Take the apple from the sink.
Go right back to the pan on the counter.
Put the apple in the pan.
Turn to the right.
Take the knife from the counter.
Turn to the left.
Cut the apple in the pan into pieces.
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple in a pan into pieces.

high_descs: Walk forward to face the stove.
Pick up the pan on the front of the stove.
Turn around and step forward and turn left to face the counter.
Place the pan on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Pick up the tomato in the sink.
Take a step to the right to face the pan on the counter.
Place the tomato on the pan on the counter.
Turn right to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn to the left to face the Pan.
Cut the tomato in the pan into slices.
anns.task_desc: To put a tomato in a pan on the counter plus cut it into slices.

high_descs: Turn right then face the stove on your left.
Take the pan off of the stove in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter with the spatula to your left.
Place the pan on the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the sink on your right.
Take the apple from the sink in front of you.
Turn right and face the counter with the pan on your left.
Place the apple in the pan on the counter in front of you.
Face the counter with the knife on your right.
Take the knife off of the counter in front of you.
Turn left and face the pan with the apple on the counter to your left.
Cut the apple in the pan on the counter in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Cut an apple on the counter.
